Date: 2024-05-01
Maintainer: Chuyao Xu  <cxu870@aucklanduni.ac.nz>
Description: This package contains some common response-adaptive randomisation methods in literatures,
             including the randomized play-the-winner rule, doubly adaptive biased coin design with minimal variance strategy and
             maximal power stategy targeting Neyman allocation and RSIHR allocation, bayesian response-adaptive randomization with 
             a control group using Thall \& Wathen method and forward-looking gittins index rule.
